The efficacy of microarray screening for autosomal recessive retinitis 
pigmentosa in routine clinical practice.

van Huet RA(1), Pierrache LH(2), Meester-Smoor MA(2), Klaver CC(3), van den Born 
LI(4), Hoyng CB(1), de Wijs IJ(5), Collin RW(6), Hoefsloot LH(7), Klevering 
